<h1>Question</h1>

<p class="ask-body">"One question I have is I know that the whole idea of the game is to be player made and community updated but i was wondering if y'all as developers plan to update the game in the future after launch to add new content?"</p>
{% include "partials/askhytale/asktwitteruser.njk" %}
